description: >-
  A short letter from a departing founder to the board of directors of a
  Delaware corporation resigning from every officer and director position held,
  with an explicit effective date. The effective date is load-bearing: it fixes
  the termination date that starts the repurchase-option window under the
  founder's existing Restricted Stock Purchase Agreement. Drafted as a starting
  point for licensed counsel review.
