# Founder Resignation Letter

{% field name="resignation_effective_date" /%}

To the Board of Directors of {% field name="company_legal_name" /%}, a Delaware corporation (the "Company"):

{% agreement-section type="cover_terms" %}
## Key Terms

{% cover-terms %}
{% cover-term kind="row" label="Company" field="company_legal_name" /%}
{% cover-term kind="row" label="Founder" field="founder_name" /%}
{% cover-term kind="row" label="Effective Date" field="resignation_effective_date" /%}
{% cover-term kind="row" label="Positions Resigned" field="resigned_positions" /%}
{% /cover-terms %}
{% /agreement-section %}
{% agreement-section type="standard_terms" %}
## Terms

{% clause id="resignation" %}
### Resignation

I, {% field name="founder_name" /%} (the "Founder"), hereby resign from all positions I hold with the Company, including {% field name="resigned_positions" /%}, effective as of {% field name="resignation_effective_date" /%} (the "Effective Date").

My resignation from the Board of Directors and each officer position is effective on the Effective Date. From and after the Effective Date, I will hold no officer or director position with the Company and will have no authority to act for or bind the Company.

{% /clause %}
{% clause id="irrevocable-and-complete" %}
### Irrevocable and Complete

This resignation is irrevocable and covers every officer and director position I hold with the Company, whether or not listed above. It is not conditioned on any action by the Company and takes effect on the Effective Date without acceptance by the Board.

{% /clause %}
{% clause id="reservation-of-rights" %}
### No Waiver of Vested Rights or Indemnification

Nothing in this letter waives, releases, or diminishes any right I have that survives my departure, including any vested equity, accrued and unpaid compensation or expense reimbursement, rights under any equity or benefit plan, or any right to indemnification, advancement of expenses, or coverage under the Company's directors-and-officers liability insurance for acts or omissions in my former capacities. This letter does not create, and shall not be read to create, any new non-competition, non-solicitation, or other post-separation restrictive covenant; any such covenant, if any, exists only under a separate written agreement.

{% /clause %}
{% /agreement-section %}
{% agreement-section type="signature" %}
## Signature

{% signature-block arrangement="entity-plus-individual" %}

Sincerely,

{% signer id="founder" kind="individual" capacity="personal" label="Founder" %}
Signature: _______________

Print Name: {% field name="founder_name" /%}

Date: {% field name="resignation_effective_date" /%}
{% /signer %}
{% /signature-block %}
{% /agreement-section %}
